title: Boeing names its new Apollo-style spacecraft the Starliner - KATC-TV Lafayette
text:
The aviation and aerospace giant announced the name of its future space fleet Friday. More than 200 people gathered at Florida's Kennedy Space Center to celebrate the grand opening of Boeing's commercial crew and cargo processing facility.
